---
title: Cheese Tortellini and Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto Sauce with Blistered Tomatoes and Spinach
description: Featuring creamy sun-dried tomato pesto sauce, baby tomatoes and Parmesan, this dish combines fresh, summer flavours with the wintery comforts of hearty pasta for the best of all seasons.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tortellinis-au-fromage-et-sauce-au-pesto-de-tomates-sechees-69ce2af2.jpg
